## Verification

- [ ] `detectFramework("/path/to/nextjs-server-app")` returns `{ framework: "nextjs", nextMode: "server", buildCommand: "pnpm build", outputDir: ".next" }`
- [ ] `detectFramework("/path/to/nextjs-static-app")` returns `{ framework: "nextjs", nextMode: "static", buildCommand: "pnpm build", outputDir: "out" }`
- [ ] `detectFramework("/path/to/dockerized-app")` returns `{ framework: "dockerfile", buildCommand: "", outputDir: "." }`
- [ ] `detectFramework("/path/to/static-site")` returns `{ framework: "static", buildCommand: "", outputDir: "." }`
- [ ] `detectFramework("/path/to/empty-dir")` throws `"Could not detect framework"`
- [ ] `detectPackageManager("/path/with/pnpm-lock.yaml")` returns `"pnpm"`
- [ ] `detectPackageManager("/path/with/package-lock.json")` returns `"npm"`
- [ ] `detectPackageManager("/path/with/yarn.lock")` returns `"yarn"`
- [ ] `detectPackageManager("/path/with/bun.lockb")` returns `"bun"`
- [ ] `detectPackageManager("/path/with/no-lockfile")` returns `"pnpm"` (default)
- [ ] Next.js config with `output: 'export'` using single quotes is detected
- [ ] Next.js config with `output: "export"` using double quotes is detected
- [ ] Next.js config files with `.js`, `.ts`, and `.mjs` extensions are all checked
- [ ] `pnpm typecheck` passes with no errors
